<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>---
</span><span class='line'>layout: page
</span><span class='line'>title: "404 Error"
</span><span class='line'>comments: false
</span><span class='line'>sharing: false
</span><span class='line'>footer: false
</span><span class='line'>---
</span><span class='line'>Whoops, the page you’re looking for cannot be found.
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>Maybe you can find what you are looking for in the [archives](/blog/archives/).</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>View <a href="http://james-ball.co.uk/404/">my 404 page</a> here.</p>
]]></content>
